<item>
            <title>[FELIX-5505] ConfigSpiOSGi may miss out on registering some LoginModuleFactory due to race condition</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FELIX-5505</link>
                <project id="12310100" key="FELIX">Felix</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;&lt;tt&gt;ConfigSpiOsgi&lt;/tt&gt; currently looks for &lt;tt&gt;LoginModuleFactory&lt;/tt&gt; and upon registration of any factory it recreates its &lt;tt&gt;Realm&lt;/tt&gt; state. &lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This logic has a race condition where concurrent addition of &lt;tt&gt;LoginModuleFactory&lt;/tt&gt; may lead to some of them getting missed from getting registered in the Realm&lt;/p&gt;</description>
